Class GroupBuilder<T extends ParsedQuery,E extends SupportsGroups>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.rdf4j.queryrender.builder.GroupBuilder<T,E>
  • Deprecated. 
    use SparqlBuilder instead.

public class GroupBuilder<T extends ParsedQuery,E extends SupportsGroups>
